IMDb summary

"In order to recover his ship impounded by the British,former pirate captain LaRochelle agrees to spy on the notorious Caribbean Sea pirates Blackbeard and Anne Providence."

My notes,

  This is a recode of "Anne of the Indies."  The character name is Anne Providence, not Ann Bonny,  noted woman pirate character of that period..  The original fileshare was 1.7 Gb.  The DVD is not available in US markets as NTSC.   Since it is a title which keeps getting hits, this version should appeal to those viewing on smaller screens.

  There's a wiki for the film.  It indicates that Jean Crane did all her own swordplay for this production.

Smaller file sizes encourage better sharing.  Once seeded I will keep this one going.

Notes written May 2, 2015
